5d6184bd8ccb9159dd38da5938173550.sql_template:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS nombre_eleves_{PrenomFr} 
FROM inscriptioneleve

12e1f5dc3784df16d727bcb9b638302d.sql_template:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS nombre_eleves_inscrits
FROM inscriptioneleve
WHERE AnneeScolaire = (SELECT id FROM anneescolaire WHERE AnneeScolaire = '2024/2025')

ba0a7d3ff96c12cfcd7273fd358dbdea.sql_template:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS nombre_eleves_inscrits 
FROM inscriptioneleve

7bd0d038486cd6389f0fa720f066c5dc.sql_template:
SELECT e.id AS id_eleve, p.NomFr AS nom, p.PrenomFr AS prenom, ed.moyemati AS note
FROM eleve e
JOIN personne p ON e.IdPersonne = p.id
JOIN edumoymati ed ON e.id = ed.idenelev
WHERE CONCAT(p.NomFr, ' ', p.PrenomFr) = 'BENABDA MALAK'

d16f499b11bcfcf30c5885ca091f4b99.sql_template:
SELECT e.id AS id_eleve, p.NomFr AS nom, p.PrenomFr AS prenom
FROM eleve e
JOIN personne p ON e.IdPersonne = p.id
JOIN inscriptioneleve i ON e.id = i.Eleve
JOIN anneescolaire a ON i.AnneeScolaire = a.id
WHERE a.AnneeScolaire = {AnneeScolaire}

e21bd037d778073a84bd54cbd14c3feb.sql_template:
SELECT p.NomFr, p.PrenomFr, e.DateNaissance, e.LieuNaissance, e.IdEdusrv 
FROM eleve e 
JOIN personne p ON e.IdPersonne = p.id 
WHERE e.IdEdusrv IN (
    SELECT id 
    FROM inscriptioneleve 
    WHERE AnneeScolaire = (SELECT id FROM anneescolaire WHERE AnneeScolaire = '2023/2024')
)

b300d9b5f9214508f35f75ba06b78922.sql_template: SELECT AnneeScolaire FROM anneescolaire WHERE Actif = 1

6e3c77f3b5218bdfc2e878b0bd31c5d3.sql_template:
SELECT p.NomFr, p.PrenomFr, e.DateNaissance 
FROM eleve e 
JOIN personne p ON e.IdPersonne = p.id 
WHERE p.Localite = (SELECT IDLOCALITE FROM localite WHERE LIBELLELOCALITEFR = 'Cebalet Ben Ammar')

ebdb386f0071de230f36626f130a66d8.sql_template:
SELECT p.NomFr, p.PrenomFr, e.DateNaissance, e.LieuNaissance 
FROM eleve e
JOIN personne p ON e.IdPersonne = p.id
JOIN inscriptioneleve ie ON e.id = ie.Eleve
JOIN niveau n ON ie.Classe = n.id
WHERE n.NOMNIVFR = '6 ème'

6b3343d7f1a45b2e5abd3423dfccc498.sql_template:
SELECT 
    i.Date, 
    COUNT(i.Eleve) AS nombre_inscriptions 
FROM 
    inscriptioneleve i 
GROUP BY 
    i.Date 
ORDER BY 
    i.Date
